A TASK MANAGMENT API

FEATURES
===================================================
-->USER AUTHENTICATION
-->USERS CAN CREAT, UPDATE, DELETE TASK
-->USERS CHANGE TASK STATUS TO COMPLETE
-->USERS CAN LIST ALL CREATED TASK


ROUTES
==================================================
POST /auth/register                     register a user accept. inputs (username, password) 
POST /auth/login                        login a user accept. inputs (username, password) 
POST /tasks                              create tasks. inputs (title, description) 
GET /tasks                              get all tasks 
PUT /tasks/[id]                         update task by id
PUT /tasks/completed/[id]                changed task status to complet
DELETE /tasks/[id]                       delete task by id